data.description: Very well maintained home in the heart of Peachtree City near Lake Peachtree! This Sweetwater Oaks Subdivision consists of one street and is admirable for its beautiful homes and no HOA!  Featuring 4 Bedrooms with 2.5 Baths * Enter the Main Level with a Two Story Entry Foyer * Formal Living Room/Office * Formal Dining Room * Family Room with Fireplace, Surround Sound and Plantation Shutters * Guest Half Bath * Kitchen with Granite, 2 Pantries + a Closet (Great Storage!) Center Prep Island, Breakfast Area and New Stainless Appliances * Laundry Room * Front and also Rear Staircases Lead you Upstairs to the Bedrooms * Spacious Owner's Suite with Owner's Bathroom including Double Sinks, Tub, Separate Shower, Walk-In Closet * 3 additional good sized Bedrooms and a full sized Bathroom * Awesome Large Bonus Room also has access to the Rear Staircase. The Backyard is a gardener's paradise with many flowers and bushes to bloom in Spring and Summer!  The yard has an irrigation system. There is also a "She-Shed" or "Gardner's Shed" being used for storage.  The roof is newer, the mechanicals are also newer (HVAC and Water Heater) and this home has 30 NEW Windows! Come visit this well maintained home, but please use all COVID protocol when entering the home.  Masks are required - Shoe covers and hand sanitizer are also provided at the front door!
